    <item>
      <title>高盛根据零售销售和就业数据下调美国经济衰退风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/goldman-cuts-us-recession-risk-following-retail-sales-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团经济学家根据本周的零售额和失业救济申请数据，将未来一年美国经济衰退的可能性从 25% 下调至 20%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/goldman-cuts-us-recession-risk-following-retail-sales-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 17:43:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
